    <lb n="1"/>Ζήνων Κρότωι χαίρειν. ὡς ἂν τάχιστα λάβηις τὴν ἐπιστολήν, 


    <lb n="2"/>λαβὲ παρὰ Πάσιτος τοῦ Ἰουδαίου ἐρίων <expan>μν<ex cert="high">ᾶς</ex></expan> <num value="25">κε</num> καὶ ἀπέγδος Ἀρτεμι-

    <lb n="3"/>δώρωι ἵνα κατασκευάσηι στρωμάτιον, ὥστε τῶι μήκει ἐπὶ δίεδρον 

    <lb n="4"/>ἢ μικρῶι μεῖζον, διπρόσωπον· χρεία γὰρ αὐτοῦ ἐστιν ὥστε Πισικλεῖ· 

    <lb n="5"/>καὶ ὡς ἂν τάχιστα γένηται, ἀπόστειλον εἰς Μέμφιν πρὸς Ἀρτεμί-

    <lb n="6"/>δωρον, καὶ πειράθητι ὅπως ἐν <expan>ἡμ<ex cert="high">έραις</ex></expan> <num value="15">ιε</num> γένηται. γεγράφαμεν δὲ 

    <lb n="7"/>καὶ Πάσι δοῦναί σοι τὰ ἔρια. 

    <lb n="8"/>ἔρρωσο. <expan><ex cert="high">ἔτους</ex></expan> <num value="33">λγ</num>, Ἐπεὶφ <num value="28">κη</num>. 
</ab></div><div type="textpart" n="v" org="uniform" part="N" sample="complete"><ab part="N">

    <lb n="9"/>Κρότωι. </ab></div></div><div n="meta.886" type="description" org="uniform" part="N" sample="complete"><p><rs type="material" cert="high">Papyrus</rs></p></div><div n="meta.886" type="commentary" subtype="textDate" org="uniform" part="N" sample="complete"><p><date type="textDate" value="-0253-09-17" notBefore="-253" notAfter="-253">17. Sept. 253 v.Chr.</date></p></div><div n="meta.886" type="bibliography" subtype="principalEdition" org="uniform" part="N" sample="complete"><listBibl default="NO"><bibl type="publication" subtype="principal" default="NO"><title level="s" type="abbreviated">P.Cair. Zen.</title><biblScope type="volume">2</biblScope><biblScope type="numbers">59241</biblScope></bibl><bibl type="Trismegistos" default="NO"><biblScope type="numbers">886</biblScope></bibl><bibl type="DDbDP" default="NO"><series>0092</series>; <biblScope type="volume">2</biblScope>; <biblScope type="numbers">59241</biblScope></bibl></listBibl><p>Perseus links: <xref type="Perseus" href="0092;2;59241" evaluate="all" from="ROOT" targOrder="Y" to="DITTO">Text in Perseus</xref></p></div><div n="meta.886" type="bibliography" subtype="corrections" org="uniform" part="N" sample="complete"><head>BL-Einträge nach BL-Konkordanz</head><listBibl default="NO"><bibl type="BL" default="NO"><biblScope type="volume">VIII</biblScope>, S. <biblScope type="pages">78</biblScope></bibl><bibl type="BL" default="NO"><biblScope type="volume">IX</biblScope>, S. <biblScope type="pages">52</biblScope></bibl></listBibl></div><div n="meta.886" type="bibliography" subtype="illustrations" org="uniform" part="N" sample="complete"><p><bibl type="illustration" default="NO">Pl. XVII (Rekto)</bibl><bibl type="illustration" default="NO">Seider, Paläographie III, 1, II Abb. 36 a, S. 204 und II Abb. 36, S. 205 und S. 315, 4</bibl></p></div><div n="meta.886" type="bibliography" subtype="otherPublications" org="uniform" part="N" sample="complete"><head>Andere Publikationen</head><listBibl default="NO"><b